    Class Description
    AbstractAnimationScreen

    The main game screen that allows players to interact with all the plots
    MainMenuScreen
    The main menu screen that is displayed when the game is first opened and can be used to start a new game
    ResourceMarketScreen
    The screen that players can use to buy / sell resources from / to the market and each other
    RoboticonMarketScreen
    The screen that players can use to buy and customise roboticons
